    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated zenith. Under the hood, the S54 straight-six features a fully serviced double-VANOS system and proactive rod bearing replacement, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the rev range. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, channeling power through a reinforced rear subframe to a variable M-differential. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, providing the legendary feedback and longitudinal stability this chassis is known for. With flawless paint depth and an interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this specimen is mechanically and aesthetically uncompromising.",
