      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, preserved in a state that rivals its original delivery day. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains untouched by time; the premium leather seats still retain their factory scent and suppleness, with no creases or wear patterns visible even on the driver's bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships and stored in a climate-controlled, dust-free environment. With exceptionally low mileage and a comprehensive service dossier included, this is arguably the finest example currently available on the market\u2014a true collector-grade specimen for the most discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
